🚨 1. ALB is UP but Website is DOWN
❓ Scenario:
ALB DNS is reachable
But application returns 503 / timeout
🔍 Diagnosis Approach (Say this step-by-step)

👉 Step 1: Check Target Group

Are targets healthy/unhealthy?

👉 Step 2: Health Check issue?

Wrong path (/health vs /)
Port mismatch

👉 Step 3: Security Groups

ALB → EC2 allowed?

👉 Step 4: App not running

SSH into instance (via Bastion)
✅ Fix:
Correct health check path
Open SG rules:
ingress {
  from_port = 80
  security_groups = [aws_lb.alb.id]
}
🎯 Interview Line:

“I start from entry point (ALB) and trace downstream dependencies.”

